title: DrinkabiliTea Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, American, Chinese, Juice bar, Take-out, Taiwanese, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A beverages cafe also offering a menu of healthy food options. On the drinks list are a selection of Chinese teas, bubble tea, smoothies, juices, and slushies. Food for vegan and vegetarians include wraps and burgers using organic sprouted whole wheat bun with fillings like organic tempeh, tofu, portobello mushroom, and eggplant. Vegans could also get appetizers like guacamole, edamame, and fresh fruit.
